# Bugbot (this silo)

Bookfellow www git root is **`/mnt/DataStore/Ventures/bookfellow/bookfellow-www`**. Not the parent `bookfellow/` folder, not hub.

## Invoke

```bash
python3 /mnt/DataStore/home/agent/scripts/hub-bugbot-gate.py invoke \
  --checkpoint CP1 \
  --plan /mnt/DataStore/Ventures/bookfellow/bookfellow-www/.cursor/plans/<plan>.plan.md
```

Use `runs[].task` **verbatim**. Expect `Full Repository Path: /mnt/DataStore/Ventures/bookfellow/bookfellow-www`.

CP2: `--changed` paths under this tree (absolute or relative to this silo).

## Do not

- Pass a hub CreatePlan twin under `/mnt/DataStore/home/agent/.cursor/plans/` — that keeps Bugbot on the hub
- Use `Full Repository Path: /mnt/DataStore`, `/mnt/DataStore/home/agent`, or the parent `…/bookfellow` (parent is not a git repo)
- Hand-roll Task params (still use gate `invoke`)
